<h1>Welcome to the Environmental Laboratory Informatics and Management System</h1>
<p>This is your one-stop shop for the Environmental Engineering (ENE) Lab. With this system, you can:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Request to use the ENE lab</li>
    <li>Review your old requests and make changes to existing ones</li>
    <li>Search the lab's chemical inventory. If there's something wrong, like we're out of a chemical but the inventory says it's still in stock, submit a correction!</li>
    <li>Manage your account</li>
    <li>Reach out to Lab Management if you have any questions or concerns about the lab</li>
</ul>
<p>So please, take a look around, and if you have any questions, feel free to contact us!</p>

